# Ponytail local settings

Default intensity: **full**. Say "ponytail lite" or "ponytail ultra" to override. Say "stop ponytail" or "normal mode" to turn off.

While **teach** or **grilling** skills are active, ponytail is suspended per those skills. Re-arm with "ponytail full" when moving to implementation.
